{"word":"ἐμφανίζω","slug":"ἐμφανίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐμφανίζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:φαίνω\">φαίνω</a></el>; ‘make readily perceptible’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> make visible <a href='B:500 14:22'>J 14:22</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b>appear <a href='B:470 27:53'>Mt 27:53</a>; <a href='B:650 9:24'>Hb 9:24</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘provide information’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> inform <a href='B:510 23:15'>Ac 23:15</a>, <a href='B:510 23:22'>22</a>; <a href='B:650 11:14'>Hb 11:14</a></b> (make clear); <b>make known,</b> of self-revelation to a select group <b><a href='B:500 14:21'>J 14:21</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> inform,</b> in adversarial context <b><a href='B:510 24:1'>Ac 24:1</a>; <a href='B:510 25:15'>25:15</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐμφανής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔμφοβος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}